（"星条旗永不落"）

818
00:48:03,589 --> 00:48:06,673
["The Stars And Stripes Forever"]

819
00:48:11,427 --> 00:48:15,720
[Humming Along]

820
00:48:16,290 --> 00:48:18,370
打得太快了,拉斯先生!
- You're ahead, Mr. Russ! - [Beating Out Of Rhythm]

821
00:48:25,550 --> 00:48:27,870
跟着拍子,拉斯先生!
Get on the beat, Mr. Russ.

822
00:48:32,390 --> 00:48:35,220
停,停,停…
Bum, ba, bum, ba... Whoa, whoa, stop, stop.

