不少人没有节拍概念
Enough of us here already think that time is a magazine.

827
00:48:45,780 --> 00:48:48,400
你也不要再雪上加霜,顺便说一句...

828
00:48:48,500 --> 00:48:54,820
巴尔先生,演奏中倾倒乐器里的口水
And I don't want you confusing us any further. And by the way...

829
00:48:49,867 --> 00:48:54,201
Mr. Barr, it is not...

830
00:48:55,080 --> 00:48:58,070
是一件很失礼的事…
as they say, considered couth...

831
00:48:56,287 --> 00:49:00,247
to empty your spit valve in the middle of the performance...

832
00:48:58,910 --> 00:49:01,970
尤其倒在邻座同学的脚上
especially not on the foot of the person sitting next to you.

833
00:49:02,460 --> 00:49:06,620
我们从头再来,一,二,一,二

834
00:49:04,208 --> 00:49:06,417
Okay, let's, uh, take it again from the top.

835
00:49:06,418 --> 00:49:08,502
One, two, one, two.

836
00:49:14,381 --> 00:49:16,422
Bum-bum-bum

837
00:49:15,930 --> 00:49:20,220
噢,噢!噢,噢!停,停!
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!

838
00:49:19,218 --> 00:49:22,552
Whoa, whoa, whoa! Stop, stop, stop.

839
00:49:22,520 --> 00:49:27,560
铃声救了你们!明天同一时间同一地点见,谢谢!
[Bell Rings]

840
00:49:24,470 --> 00:49:27,220
Boy, were you saved by the bell. All right, same time...

841
00:49:27,222 --> 00:49:29,263
same place tomorrow.

842
00:49:29,530 --> 00:49:35,060
-霍兰先生,我想让你知道... -你会很努力,我知道
Thank you very much.

843
00:49:31,308 --> 00:49:34,058
Mr. Holland, look, I just want you to know that...

844
00:49:35,200 --> 00:49:37,820
-谢谢,霍兰先生 -不客气
That you're gonna work very hard. I know, Louis. Thank you.

845
00:49:36,853 --> 00:49:39,770
- Thanks, Mr. Holland. - You're welcome.

846
00:49:39,910 --> 00:49:44,120
说说你巡回演出时的艳遇吧!
