847
00:49:44,210 --> 00:49:47,790
那是不同的年代,不同的我
- That was a different time. I was a very different guy. - Mm-hmm.

848
00:49:47,920 --> 00:49:49,960
将军!
- Check. - [Exhales]

849
00:49:49,568 --> 00:49:53,068
Oh, you must be keepin' something so good for me...

850
00:49:51,380 --> 00:49:53,950
你一定对我隐瞒着什么

851
00:49:54,050 --> 00:49:57,000
你总是躲避这类话题
because you're always avoiding this line of questioning.

852
00:49:57,140 --> 00:49:59,840
我没有躲避,只是我已过上另一种生活
- [Laughs] I'm not avoiding anything. - I know you are.

853
00:49:59,970 --> 00:50:04,130
我有美丽的妻子,可爱的小孩,你不了解的
- It's just, I lead a very different life now. - Uh-huh.

854
00:50:01,117 --> 00:50:06,660
I have a beautiful wife, a gorgeous child. Something you know nothing about. Check.

855
00:50:04,220 --> 00:50:05,970
将军

856
00:50:06,020 --> 00:50:09,470
-有一天我也会有孩子 -你要先娶个老婆
