857
00:50:09,610 --> 00:50:11,640
我没那么急迫

858
00:50:11,456 --> 00:50:14,289
- I don't want kids that badly. - [Laughs]

859
00:50:13,070 --> 00:50:15,140
将军,死棋
Checkmate.

860
00:50:16,440 --> 00:50:19,060
好吧 好吧
[Sighs] All right, all right, all right.

861
00:50:19,200 --> 00:50:22,200
何况,学校的孩子就像我的儿女

862
00:50:20,837 --> 00:50:24,546
Besides, the kids at school are like my kids.

863
00:50:22,910 --> 00:50:27,620
有时我也想揍他们 但更希望他们有出息

864
00:50:24,548 --> 00:50:29,216
I wanna smack 'em sometimes, but mostly I just want to see 'em do good.

865
00:50:28,330 --> 00:50:30,620
卢拉斯能不能加入军乐队?
So, Lou Russ. He gonna make it?

866
00:50:32,920 --> 00:50:34,990
有没有可能?

867
00:50:34,428 --> 00:50:36,428
Is he gonna make it?

868
00:50:36,300 --> 00:50:39,880
-我看是不行. -别这样,我需要他!
