872
00:50:46,640 --> 00:50:48,960
不关摔跤的事,我是关心他
It's not about wrestling. I care about the kid.

873
00:50:49,060 --> 00:50:52,510
他不会乐器,我怎么留他?

874
00:50:50,688 --> 00:50:54,188
Bill, how am I supposed to keep a kid in the band if he can't play an instrument?

875
00:50:52,650 --> 00:50:56,180
你教他呀!像拉斯这么努力的孩子

876
