879
00:51:01,150 --> 00:51:04,240
-教不会呀! -那你是个不称职的老师
- No, no, you teach him. - I tried and I can't.

880
00:51:05,450 --> 00:51:10,190
我不能坐视他错过机会
Well, then, you're a lousy teacher.

881
00:51:07,031 --> 00:51:12,241
And I just can't see a chance like this gettin' away from him if I can stop it.

882
00:51:15,370 --> 00:51:17,700
我年青时也跟他一样

883
00:51:17,960 --> 00:51:23,250
要不是有人给我机会发挥所长
Look, I was a kid just like him.

884
00:51:19,163 --> 00:51:24,998
And if someone hadn't given me a chance to excel in the one thing I was good at...

885
00:51:23,380 --> 00:51:28,370
我永远不会像现在这样 成为一名出色的教练

886
00:51:25,000 --> 00:51:29,959
I never would have become the brilliant gum-chewing coach that I am.

887
00:51:29,961 --> 00:51:32,045
[Chuckles]

888
00:51:35,600 --> 00:51:39,380
象棋队一直不收我,毁了我的生活
I was kept off the chess team, and, well, it's ruined my life.

