[Male Newscaster] The mood was silence and reverence...

1618
01:45:49,030 --> 01:45:53,070
“当人们唱起约翰?列侬的歌时”
at the appointed hour of 11:00.

1619
01:45:49,851 --> 01:45:53,768
But as the crowd continued singing the Beatles' songs... the songs of John Lennon...

1620
01:45:53,160 --> 01:45:55,910
“现场气氛热烈、振奋、充满活力”
they became happier, vibrant, more spirited.

1621
01:45:55,990 --> 01:46:00,410
“或许这正是列侬一生奋斗的目的”
