1622
01:46:00,500 --> 01:46:02,320
“这是吉米?柯林斯在波特兰报导”
At O'Bryan Square in southwest Portland, this is Jim Collins reporting.

1623
01:46:02,860 --> 01:46:05,819
[Dog Barking]

1624
01:46:32,400 --> 01:46:34,610
你的眼睛怎么了?
What happened to your eye?

1625
01:46:36,740 --> 01:46:38,810
什么?
Sorry?

