01:46:45,040 --> 01:46:46,990
等会儿再说
Later. [Tool Clanks]

1627
01:46:51,800 --> 01:46:54,330
等一会儿!
In a second!

1628
01:47:00,930 --> 01:47:04,790
有人被...杀了
Someone was... was killed.

1629
01:47:05,850 --> 01:47:09,100
不,柯尔,那并不好笑
No, no, Cole. That's not funny.

1630
01:47:20,910 --> 01:47:22,940
约翰…
John...

1631
01:47:25,710 --> 01:47:27,330
列侬
Lennon.

1632
01:47:27,620 --> 01:47:29,660
一个音乐人
The musician.

1633
01:47:30,327 --> 01:47:34,411
[Sighs Deeply] You wouldn't understand.

1634
