柯尔,怎么回事?
[Exhales] Cole, what is it?

1638
01:48:00,190 --> 01:48:03,810
-他要干什么? -他有话要说
He wants to what?

1639
01:48:01,680 --> 01:48:04,263
He wants to tell you something. He wants to be sure you understand.

1640
01:48:03,950 --> 01:48:07,110
-不能以后再说吗? -现在就说!
- Couldn't we do this another time? - Now!

1641
